{"tid":958193,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"范國威印月曆被當廢紙賣　","createTime":"2018-12-27T15:10:16.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-27T16:08:35.000Z","uid":79563,"like":7,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"8a38204e72e237757ad0a21951f79991cc513fcc","tid":958193,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-27T15:10:16.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/港聞/article/20181227/s00001/1545906622776/【emily-online】印月曆被當廢紙賣-范國威-感嘆香港多貧窮基層\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E%2Farticle%2F20181227%2Fs00001%2F1545906622776%2F%E3%80%90emily-online%E3%80%91%E5%8D%B0%E6%9C%88%E6%9B%86%E8%A2%AB%E7%95%B6%E5%BB%A2%E7%B4%99%E8%B3%A3-%E8%8C%83%E5%9C%8B%E5%A8%81-%E6%84%9F%E5%98%86%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E5%A4%9A%E8%B2%A7%E7%AA%AE%E5%9F%BA%E5%B1%A4&d=fzv%2B2vYWJBcjxCXyavB6NWi1w7%2FDyS2Kz%2BsYtkalU0Y%3D&h=bb9be81f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E%2Farticle%2F20181227%2Fs00001%2F1545906622776%2F%E3%80%90emily-online%E3%80%91%E5%8D%B0%E6%9C%88%E6%9B%86%E8%A2%AB%E7%95%B6%E5%BB%A2%E7%B4%99%E8%B3%A3-%E8%8C%83%E5%9C%8B%E5%A8%81-%E6%84%9F%E5%98%86%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E5%A4%9A%E8%B2%A7%E7%AA%AE%E5%9F%BA%E5%B1%A4&h=7a28f960\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/ins/港聞/article/20181227/s00001/1545906622776/【emily-online】印月曆被當廢紙賣-范國威-感嘆香港多貧窮基層</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20181227/s00001/58213ebcd8117ff49e163f6494966241.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20181227%2Fs00001%2F58213ebcd8117ff49e163f6494966241.jpg&h=243a299c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n年尾又係各個政團向街坊派發月曆嘅時候，有網民就喺fb上載照片，顯示多本新民主同盟立法會議員范國威（Gary）派發嘅月曆，疑似被棄置。身在外地嘅Gary同Emily講，相信佢啲月曆唔係被棄置，而係有長者重複排隊拎完佢嘅工作報告同月曆後，賣畀廢紙回收站。<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nGary引述有街坊報料佢聽，話見到有長者拎完佢啲工作報告同月曆後，賣畀廢紙收賣站。佢話今年一共印咗幾萬本月曆，估計每個議員不時派發嗰啲單張、工作報告或者月曆，都有大約3%至4%，畀人拎去賣畀廢紙回收。佢就曾經勸喻過啲重複攞工作報告嘅公公婆婆，叫佢哋唔好拎第3次；仲話早上見到公公婆婆拎住環保袋、好似見到寶咁走埋嚟攞單張，有時都會心感不妙。<br />\n<br />\n讀設計出身嘅Gary仲相當熟行情，話月曆內頁只係128g嘅啞粉紙，燙金福字塊卡紙就係兩張350g雙粉卡貼埋一齊，所以塊卡紙先最值錢咁話。<br />\n<br />\nGary透露，一本月曆印製成本大約4.5元。對於月曆畀人咁樣處置，佢話有少少難受；另外佢亦都有啲無奈，因為派發工作報告，係議員交代工作嘅一個重要途徑，但冇辦法阻止公公婆婆攞去賣。同時佢都感嘆話，香港有好多貧窮基層。"},{"pid":"f3ada8bc95205844278ddba7f7fd5c0dcb0e3ac7","tid":958193,"uid":38904,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-27T15:13:21.000Z","msg":"唔當佢係垃圾算係畀足面佢啦?<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8a907be6798682da898863b2da6dd86485bfd5b7","tid":958193,"uid":84751,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-27T15:15:42.000Z","msg":"成班死廢老<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n去工賊會拎果d course booklet仲好啦, 大把任佢拎"},{"pid":"5ec7737b01af50b311c14d257a9363ee5b4bb366","tid":958193,"uid":56698,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"8a907be6798682da898863b2da6dd86485bfd5b7","tid":958193,"uid":84751,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-27T15:15:42.000Z","msg":"成班死廢老<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n去工賊會拎果d course booklet仲好啦, 大把任佢拎"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-27T15:20:13.000Z","msg":"本課程簡介厚到爆 拎去賣就正<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c2c4182aef59f7733c94d9e014063df22b374733","tid":958193,"uid":64056,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-27T15:24:34.000Z","msg":"立法會議員印月曆嗰啲錢咪又係公帑<br />\n廢老又然<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f365104ffaebb88974e9fd2044d89b25ac8c7593","tid":958193,"uid":64874,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5ec7737b01af50b311c14d257a9363ee5b4bb366","tid":958193,"uid":56698,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"p